{
  "stem": "8423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took a red crayon and he marked my forehead, like a little cross on my-- on my forehead.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as soon as he turned, he-- oh, so he said to my sister, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She'll be one of the first ones we take.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I was already really like out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as soon he turned his head, she took some spittle, real quick, put it on my forehead, put her forehead on top of mine, like a blotter, lied down next to me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, I'm not gonna let them separate us now, after all that we've been together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says, I'm going with you when they come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sure enough, then they came, we got on the same stretcher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took us to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was unconscious for weeks there before, you know, they nursed me back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was pretty much chaotic, except that they did have this roll call in the morning, cell appel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they collected the dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made the prisoners collect them and take them, you know, to the piles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we still got that one meal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I told you, it was so sparse, that half the time the bucket wound up on the floor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody got any.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because one person would rush it, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was spilled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was just horrendous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germans not care the last day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The night before, the very night before we were liberated, we heard rumors that, you know, we were going to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then as we were listening, we could hear gunshots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the gunshots were coming closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we realized, OK, this is it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Camp is going to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Russians must be close.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
